  <description>
    <p>A fully reverse engineered PC port of the Java mobile game based on the 90s
        retro shooter.</p>
    <p><em>PLEASE NOTE:</em> This Flatpak does <em>not</em> include the game data for Doom RPG.
        Please copy the file <code>Doom RPG.ipa</code> file to
        <code>$HOME/.var/app/io.github.erick194.doomrpg-re/doom2rpg/</code>.</p>
    <p>Launching any of the games included will inform you with a message if any of the required
        files are missing and where you need to copy them.</p>
  </description>
